text: Katehari is a constituency of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly covering the city of Katehari in the Ambedkar Nagar district of Uttar Pradesh, India. Katehari is one of five assembly constituencies in the Ambedkar Nagar (Lok Sabha constituency) Since 2008, this assembly constituency is numbered 277 amongst 403 constituencies. ==References== Category:Assembly constituencies of Uttar Pradesh Category:Ambedkar Nagar district
